  07 Apr 2007; Bryan Drewery <bryan@shatow.net> ChangeLog:
  Also install a few docs

  07 Apr 2007; Bryan Drewery <bryan@shatow.net> ChangeLog:
  Upstream release 5.2.3
  Version 5.2.3
  
  New program irp.cpp to automatically generate optimal code for insertion
  in the reduce2(.) function in mrecgf2m.c
  The program findbase.cpp to find the "best" irreducible polynomial has
  been updated.
  New program newbasis.cpp converts a value from one irreducible polynomial
  representation to another.

  06 Apr 2007; Bryan Drewery <bryan@shatow.net> ChangeLog:
  Chmod 644 on the headers
  Use dolib.a on library

  06 Apr 2007; Bryan Drewery <bryan@shatow.net> ChangeLog:
  Simplified seds into 1 call

  06 Apr 2007; Bryan Drewery <bryan@shatow.net> ChangeLog:
  Add a mirror

  05 Apr 2007; Bryan Drewery <bryan@shatow.net> ChangeLog:
  Fix build script to use proper toolchan functions

  05 Apr 2007; Bryan Drewery <bryan@shatow.net> ChangeLog:
  Port miracl to gentoo

